<section id="command-downpitch">
<title>DOWNPITCH</title>
<indexterm><primary>DOWNPITCH</primary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>DOWN</primary></indexterm>

<variablelist>

<varlistentry><term>Synopsis</term>
<listitem>
<synopsis><command>DOWNPITCH</command> <parameter>angle</parameter>
<command>DOWN</command> <parameter>angle</parameter></synopsis>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry><term>Description</term>
<listitem>
<para>
Pitches the turtle's nose downward by the specified angle, measured in degrees (1/360 of a circle).
</para>
<para>
This command is designed to run in <link linkend="command-perspective">PERSPECTIVE</link> mode.
</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry><term>Example</term>
<listitem>
<programlisting><userinput>PERSPECTIVE
DOWNPITCH 45
REPEAT 3 [FORWARD 100 LEFT 120]</userinput>
</programlisting>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

</variablelist>

</section>
